+ animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Asymmetry: averting intense suffering takes priority over creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx9Vm1v4kgM%2FisWutNBRWmgpRKc%2BEBb%2BqJjb6sut6tVqdIhccjcTmaimQlprtv%2Ffp4EKBTYT6XYfmw%2FfuzhtRZixDJhL1WItX7t5AQGgwFMNOMSrIJAs%2F8K%2BpBLmGYdr30GudIiXHDMIW%2F7Hf%2FUP%2FO7%2FjnUjVUpnDdc%2BFQSzNCYLEktVxKCmND64EHKtApizoQDa%2Fc60IaIaZ%2FlrPDjLGHSrAwdYJInTBjfqATzmNmV5RSizGYalwF%2BwqxF7efcxn7ITaAyabmcr9zPQKrN7%2F2t6JVXd51uCcd8odYpz8FkUYS6DFdBZjAsWxyxIAb23ic3wOC%2BsDF9jrhAIA7fzeYErOuDhaFpgkYinks0oHQJpvGY6GEJUnpu6HsbY8XcH4ZalkGJ8ScEKkmVcR2uHShWhkiI9BU3JZqxTIZMKImQ0GRFC57Xgxstnl2pLhxfUgwsBS6YyBBUVCK8z7hVgl2gsTDLCshcGhdocLOxPgzvwLAIbQH1BwxzpUJ4ICemg7hRYdyM%2Fh49DCejK5gVMEeJmllspcVKVhhyu0XWERmbNDxbleT4JKQS64prqhqQZkJ%2FiGx0g1B6TkylmuaoC5hRiogHnD434WJ0%2FflhRExoJkqEHPk8dnIgXoRyQo%2F5czU%2FoeZSadIC9Lzf4fIO6kpT18cqOk7YXHKbhQgXnyejS9eZUVn6F7dBjPKKieIe9T8mhAG8TiVAiioVeIsixXBt8Vpe1yX0Wl3nk6MQM6RKbmiQDqJy8dqVj9d2TqV4UUcssBkTF0z%2B%2BFrOy7meHsh0tAf6COptOD4E15jKt6mch1uNuFqW9XqdqWRJ9NHcqaxUKOPJTmx7bbWx2LKWllOPOMzTbYPnLF3PI1vORTjL5mbLobt2IA8mRIQ7NZfgbTLrSo7762p7XgVSrfNjfjUcfwe2QO12IiWt%2F%2FbU31RXuKU8y5Plnr4rK1BkJN2htB92icLZh5sIaWaNEzC3TkuBcjs8gEc30lcgsrEP09pYBaRGpzT4UUltWmtCHq5b6kOCTNb3arFBQyeRwFtzG%2FSGL7DaI1Hsh9sUwq9QvpHMwB1%2FaklzdwKGn64b%2BzG35ONAdyGHd5%2FgBC6XWCNpNaZ03zDTJubpAdhN4R2qdUJzunVXH2GMbJ7hfqwtmVZYvd75DtqXmA5NCtQ8vWAI91r9S1weGMymwCtIr7db4DfSOj0ZhnAM1OOq1JRuL8kpRHOA0t0NWWbYQ%2B14fD26OkDhh