;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + suffering_focused&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Asymmetry: averting intense suffering takes priority over creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 6 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx9lm1v4jgQx7%2FKCN3qoKI0gban5cQL2tIHLXtbdblbnUqVmmRCfOvYke00zXX73XecAIUC%2B6qUGf88D%2F8Z89KIMGa5sOcqwka%2FcXQEg8EAJppxCVZBqNn%2FJX0oJEzzrucfQ6G0iJ44FlD4QTfoBcfBKTSNVRmcttzhqSTI0Jg8zSxXEsKEWH3wIGNahQlnwqH8j13wIWY6YAUrgyRPmTRLQxeY5CkTJjAqxSJhdmnpQZzbXOPiQJAya1EHBbdJEHETqlxaLudL92OQav37YOP00usUTB7HqCsHFeYGoyqJEQsTYG%2BZcAMMbkub0OeYCwSq0ZvZHIF1kbIoMm3QSIXlEg0oXcE0HlIBWIoULzf0vU2wrs3vhpKSYcX4E0KVZsq4HFYOdFZGSET6ipuKZiyTERNKIqTUOdGBx1VjRk%2BPLlR3HJ8zDC0dfGIiR1BxRXjrYaeCnaGxMMtLyN017qDB9cT6MLwBw2K0JTTvMCqUiuCOnJgOk1bNuBr9NbobTkYXMCthjhI1s9jJyqVsMOJ2o1gHZGxTe2wdkqsnkSrWBdcUNSD1hP5QsdE1Quk5VSrTJAxdwoyuiHnI6XMbzkaXX%2B5GVAnNREUokM8T13Cqi1BOyAl%2FrPsn1FwqTeKCj94HOL%2BBptKU9aGKD1M2l9zmEcLZl8no3GVmVJ594jZMUF4wUd6i%2FttEMICXqQTIUGUCr1FkGK0sXsc7cRd6nRPnU6AQM6RIrqiRDlG7eH7t4%2FnOqZIn6piFNmfijMnv%2F1T9cq69PTcd7EAfQNOHw3241lS%2BTuU82kjExbKI1%2BtOJUvj9%2BZubaVAGU%2B3zvorq03EhrWy9DyqYZFtGjxnOfE8shVcRLN8bjYcTlYO5MGEiHEr5gruk1nXctwdl%2B95NaQe5%2FviYjj%2BF9gTajcTGWn9t4f%2BurqiDeVZni7m9E1ZoSIj6Q6lfTdLdJy923qQ5dY4AXPrtBQqN8MDuHctfQEqNvZh2hirkNTolAbfa6lNG20oolVKfUiRyeZOLbao6SQSeG1vQq%2F4E9ZzJMrduHUh%2FIryjWQGbr1TSpq7FTD8fNnazdyQj4NuI4c3n%2BEIzheskbQaM9pvmGuT8GwPdl14%2B2KdUJ%2Bu3V5HGCOb57ibtSHTmuWf%2BH%2F0jreAXxPaNRlQ%2FvRMIdxq9R%2BVc09v1jVeUbdw30jq9GIYYhhoJnWkGa1eUlOEZk9FtwdkN304Hl%2BOLvaU790I7avgr7b8bvLW9K2jH9zcado%2B7