nt proxy with Rethink Priorities&#x27; welfare-range estimates (Fischer et al.) and count invertebrates — shrimp, insects, and the ~10^19 soil animals. Under RP medians a chicken&#x27;s welfare range is a third of a human&#x27;s, not a fiftieth, and wild/soil invertebrates carry significant aggregate (nematode) weight, so invertebrate work dominates. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 5 animals_matter_a_lot" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJyFVm1v4kYQ%2Fisj1KoQEWKgfDgqPkAgLyrXi3K0pypEZLHHeHvrXWt3jePm8t87a%2FMajPophJl55u15ZnmrBRiyVNhrFWCtX7u6gsFgADPNuASrwNfs35w%2BZBLmacdr%2FwqZ0iJYc8wgay86i%2B6iB3VjVQK9hgudS4IYGpPGieVKgh8RUh88SJhWfsSZcEDtTx1oQ8j0gmUsX0RpzKTZGjrAJI%2BZMAujYswiZreWLoSpTTVuAhYxsxb1IuM2WgTc%2BCqVlsvV1r23A9o4soVQtqhwwvwI2L5MboDBQ24j%2BhxygUDt783mCqwrgwWBaYJGmhmXaEDpAkzjJXXHYqQc3ND3NsKy8V8MVSz9AuM38FWcKOMK3DlQrAyQEOkrbgo0Y5kMmFASIaaliBa87GY%2BWb%2B4Ul04viboWwpcM5EiqLBA2K%2BnVYCN0FhYpjmkLo0LNHjYWB%2B%2BcRFQt4bADNSLwSIkFMZ9HqBplDi3kz8mj8PZZAzLHFYoUTOLrSTfsgIDbo8GdkHGJkhly7LcTAmpwBpzTckAw9D9oYGjW4bSK5pWomlhOoclpQipAvrchNHk5svjhKahmSgQMuSryG2aZiOU42nEX8odCrWSStPS4ZP3M1zfQ11p6vxShZcxW0lu0wBh9GU2uXadGZUmv3PrRyjHTOQPqP80AQzgbS6BhqASgXcoEgx2Fq%2Fl9VxCr9VzPhkKsUSq5JaW6SBKF69d%2Bnht51TwEnXIfJsyMWLy%2B1%2FFzpxr90ymiwroC6i34fIcXGMu3%2BdyFRw14mrZ1Ot15pLF4Udzp7RSoYzHJ7HtndVG4shaWLoezTBLjg2es%2FQ8j2wZkWuZrsyRQ2%2FnQB5MiBBPai7A22QmZWRKnfa0cfBKkFLST9l4OP0b2Bq100VCfP%2FpuX%2FIruCIeZbHG63umeUrMhLvUNoPeqJw9uGsQZKSZtz1sI5LvnI6HsCTW%2Bkb0LCxD%2FPaVPnERsc0%2BF5SbV5rQhbsWupDjEzWK7nYoKW34b15DHnL11iqSOTVYIc0OI%2FxjSgG7nZTO5rbHOrDzzeNasQj6lRDDu8%2FwxVcb7Am0mpM6L5hqk3EkzOwh6Srhp3Rhu7KuzRFtkqxGumIoA6JxNXtnKB9jejEJECt0%2FOD8KDVPzTHMys5pHYJ6XVPC%2Fy%2FE1oNfqqNTYaKwU6nN5PxmQF%2BENB5kHswLES35cdSVfBIrwHTfnSmwhPxFdgF8LMTnabT416zAUy5sS2NpDyD9eIfo7Qd5fVSFE14%2B%2FH6A15bBzneG3Swlu55GsAG6Ml73mh5VvnAze7uv%2B4F2YfipwGnmS%2B3rxxJnVMVhuR48GZSBudxmH0ua%2B%2F%2FAWaXDN0%3D" id="w1_2_3_5"><mxCell style="rou