a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 7 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJyFVm1z4kYM%2Fisapp1CSogNAQIdPpCEvEy5XiZHe9MJGd9iy3h79q5ndx2H5vLfq7WB8Dr9kAlB0iPp0SNt3ioBhiyLzZUMsNKvnJ3BYDCAiWJcgJHgK%2Fbvgj7kAqZZ03HPIZcqDl445pC7XtNreW2v43Whqo1MoVuz4VNBMEOtsyQ1XArwI0LrgwMpU9KPOIstmNtrggshUx7L2cKLsoQJvTI0gQmesFh7WiaYR8ysLC0IM5MpXAZ4CTMGlZdzE3kB177MhOFivnJvr4GWjsyL5RqsAzoLQ1QU4IXSzzQGK1MXEmTGox8KSpWcxZgUjY2YHwH76I5rYPCwMBF9DnmMQMx9mPUZGFs9CwJdB4VENxeoQaoCTOEpkcISpCxc0%2FcmwpKvXzQ1KvwC4zfwZZJKbftaO1CsCJAQ6SuuCzRtmAhYLAVCQvOMG%2FBtPa7Ryzdbqg3H1xR9Q4EvLM4QZFggfEy2UYBdojYwyxaQ2TQ2UONmY334yuOAutUEpqFazAMhpTDu8wB1rcS5Hf0xehxORtcwW8AcBSqitJEuVoLCgJstwk7IWAdBUyrKspwSUoF1zRUlA6SZ0S8iHO0wpJoTW6miOasFzChFSBXQ5zpcjm4%2BP46IDcXiAiFHPo%2BsQIibWFqJR%2FxbOcNYzoVUpBXoOT%2FD1T1UpaLOT2V4mrC54CYLEC4%2FT0ZXtjMts%2FR3bvwIxTWLFw%2Bo%2FtQBDOBtKoBIkGmMdxinGKwtTsNp24ROo219cozjGVIltzRMC1G6OG7p47jWqZAzqpD5JmPxJRPf%2FypmZl1bRzKdHIA%2BgaoLp8fgalPxPhXzYKsRW8uyXqc5FSwJd83N0kqFMp7sxbprq4niLWthaTnEYZ5uGxxraTsO2XIS1yyb6y2H9tqBPFgch7hXcwHukpk2I5dyv6elg1OClCv9lF8Px38De0Fl9yIlvf%2F03N9UV7ClPMOT5a5%2BKMuXZCTdoTA7%2B0ThbOcaQprRztjrYayWfGn3eABPdqRvQGRjH6aVsfRJjVZp8L2U2rRShzxYt9S3R0pUD2qxRkMnkcCvUD21fTutbq%2FldmrwXt%2FOcstfsFyseHEYf1MZu7DdZrvTPj%2BM%2BpV0CPZdoJ4VNwuoDj%2Fd1A7n2NKXTbJO0Wqddx13P8Pw%2FhOcwdUSeiSMwpRuImZKRzw9kmVTqDutuN3OxcXFfp4JjfmuPG5jZPMMD0NvqbyE7vU6e2hfIrpTKRA19PQhPCj5DzF%2FZK6b%2B1FCOr3WHuT%2F3eHD4PsLtsywn2A4Ht%2BMro8wurOFS5BDKPegWYhWBo%2FlbsIjvSlM%2BdGREvdWuAAvgJ%2Ft6io6YPZNHMCYa9NQSPursVr8oaUyl4tquVp1ePvx%2BgNeGxs53mt09mb2kRvAEujJeV5ehMnBZ3Jyd%2F%2FlY637UPxfwon02eqtpIPBqQpNS73x8lIG67GZfSoq7%2F8BJ%2BItuQ%3D%3D" id="w1_2_3_5_6_7"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#eec2a8;strokeColor=#c65a2e;fontColor=#5a2a10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="400" y="956" width="272" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Net-negative lives&lt;br&gt;(animal suffering dominates)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+5+6+7+8]&lt;br&gt;→ Wild insects (humane pesticides)&lt;br&gt;(Brian Tomasik, David Benatar)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + meat_eater_problem + net_negative_animal_lives&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The net-negative-lives hypothesis: factory-farmed and wild animals endure more suffering than wellbeing, so their lives are not worth living. Reducing that suffering is worth more per dollar (you are mitigating a catastrophe, not improving a good life), most of all for the astronomical wild-invertebrate populations. Combined with the meat-eater problem it drives human charities firmly net-negative — every human sustained means more net-negative farmed lives. Presupposes counting wild/invertebrate animals, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot; and like the meat-eater problem it is a near-term animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans). || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 7 meat_eater_problem → 8 net_negative_animal_lives" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJyFVm1v4kYQ%2Fisj1KqQEmJDCQkVH%2FJCXnRcL8rRnqoQOYs9xttb71q76zg0l%2F%2FeWRsIb1E%2FIIxn9pmZZ56Z5bUWYcxyYS9UhLV%2B7egIBoMBjDXjEqyCULN%2F5%2FRQSJjkbc%2F%2FDQqlRfTMsYDCD9pBJ%2BgGx0EvOIG6sSqDk4YDmEgCOjMmTzPLlYQwIbw%2BeJAxrcKEM%2BHg%2FNM2%2BBAzHbCCzYMkT5k0S0MbmOQpEyYwKsUiYXZp6UCc21zj4kCQMmtRBwW3SRBxE6pcWi5nS%2FfuCmjhyAKhVmDHYPI4Rk0HgliFucFoaepBiswG9KFDmVZTgenSdgISbSBxxix%2FxqCKEAh6NmXtQxYmwN4J4AYY3M1tQs8xFwhE77vZHIF1BbIoMk3QSD3hEg0oXYJpPCTeWIqUCDf03iZYUfqLIS5kWGL8DqFKM2Vc6SsHOisjJER6xavUjGUyYkJJhJSaLlrwtOrp8PnJpeqO40uGoaWDz0zkCCouEd7b3yrBztFYmOZzyF0Yd9DgemF9%2BMZFRNUaAjNQL1uGkNExHvIITaPCuR7%2BMbw%2FGw8vYTqHGUrUxHormy9VhxG3G4QdkLEJkhpZpuU4JaQS65JrCgZIbaUvIhxdM5SeEVuZpkbpOUwpREwZ0HMTzodXX%2B6HxIZmokQokM8SpyHiRig3Bwl%2Fqnoo1EwqTc2GU%2B9nuLiFut