ditive penalty — farmed-animal life-years caused per human DALY, times the suffering per factory-farmed life-year, times the animal&#x27;s welfare range. Under a heavy animal welfare range the penalty can exceed the human benefit, so saving human lives looks net-harmful. Only bites once animals count, so it requires animals_somewhat; and it is a near-term human-vs-animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans), where x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 suffering_focused → 7 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx1Vm1z4kYM%2Fisapp1CCsSGEAIdPpCEvMxxvUyO9qYTMr7FlvH27F3P7joOzeW%2FV2vzGuADg7G0j6RHj7S8VQIMWRabKxlgpV85PYXBYAATxbgAI8FX7L8FPeQCplnLcc8glyoOXjjmkLtey2t7514XqtrIFLo1e3gqCGSodZakhksBfkRYfXAgZUr6EWexhXJ7LXAhZMpjOVt4UZYwoVeGFjDBExZrT8sE84iZlaUNYWYyhcsDXsKMQeXl3ERewLUvM2G4mK%2Fcz0FnYYiKXnmh9DONwcrUhQSZ8ehD51MlZzEmReoj5kfANvlzDQweFiai55DHCMTMxqxPwdj8WBDoOigkOrlADVIVYAobVDZLkKJwTe9NhCUjv2kqRfgFxh%2FgyySV2ma%2BdqCzIkBCpFdcF2jaMBGwWAqEhPoVN%2BH7uh2jl%2B82VXscX1P0DR18YXGGIMMCYdO5ZgF2idrALFtAZsPYgxq3C%2BvDhLDuLM8IY2TzDMuDt6M%2FR4%2FDyegaZguYo0BFHDbTxUohGHCzw9AJGesgpCnzsCQSUoF1zRWlCkhNoi9iGC37Us2JnlSRBtQCZhQi5D6n5zpcjm6%2BPI6ofMXiAiFHPo9sz4mMWFrNRvx72bRYzoVUpCPoOb%2FC1T1UpaJSGzJsJGwuuMkChMsvk9FVjfLRMks%2FceNHKK5ZvHhA9ZcOYABvUwGQokxjvMM4xWBtcZpOxwZ0mh3rk2Mcz5AyuaXuWYjSxXFLH8e1ToVCUYXMNxmLL5n48XfRJOvaPhLp5AD0CVRdaByDq03F%2B1TMg51CbC7LfJ3WVLAk%2FGhulVZKlPFk76y7tpoo3rEWlrZDHObprsGxlo7jkC3ncTDL5nrHobN2IA8WxyHu5VyAu2SmUcil3K9p6eCUIOUMP%2BXXw%2FE%2FwF5Q2UFISeC%2FPPe31RXsKM%2FwZDmcG2X5koykOxTmwwDRcfZhwUGaGW0FzI3Vki%2Ft4A7gybb0DYhs7MO0MpY%2BqdEqDX6UUptW6pAH65L6diuJ6kEt1qjpJBL4HaqNTrPbvTg%2Fw4bTqcF7fTfKLX%2FBcrDixWH8bWVswxZ0uk7nrHcY9RvpEOyqp5oVNwuoDj%2Ff1A7H2NGXDbIJ0XF6F73z%2FRDD%2B89wCldL7JEwClPagpgpHfH0SJhtpX6spXXeO%2Bte7Afa22yHsXd0XmK7HbfbPtsD%2FBrRskqB%2BKErDeFBy